Effective Date: June 1, 2025

Sheikh Jebril App ("we", "our", or "us") respects your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your information when you use our mobile application, Sheikh Jebril App.

## 1. Information We Collect

We may collect the following types of information when you use Sheikh Jebril App:

### a. Personal Information
- Email address (only if you contact support)
- User preferences for app settings

### b. Usage Data
- Audio playback information (which Surahs you listen to)
- Favorite selections and downloaded content
- Session data (duration, crash logs, performance)

### c. Device Information
- Device type, OS version, and app version
- Storage information (for download management)
- Anonymous identifiers (for analytics purposes)

## 2. How We Use Your Information

We use the collected data to:
- Provide and improve app features
- Manage downloaded audio files
- Remember your favorites and preferences
- Diagnose technical issues and improve app performance
- Communicate with users (support or updates)

## 3. Third-Party Services

